Even Across Borders, Weve Got You!

Break Boundaries, Not Payroll: Cross Border by PaidHR

Whether you're growing a global team or managing payments in multiple currencies, PaidHR makes it easy for you to pay employees across different countries and currencies, without the hassle. Expand your talent pool confidently, no borders, no barriers, just possibilities.

Get Started
Learn more
One-Click Currency Conversion, Anytime

Get real-time conversion rates at your fingertips! Know exactly how much to fund your wallet with and seamlessly swap to any currency of your choice in just one click.

Tailored Schedules by Currency

Create tailored payroll schedules based on the currency your employees earn. Optimize transactions to potentially save on conversion costs and enhance payroll efficiency.

Stay Compliant, Stay Global

We ensure you stay compliant across borders by accurately computing taxes, pensions, and other essential contributions. With our expertise, you can focus on expanding your global presence, knowing that your payroll meets all local regulations.
